<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Codeunia: The Definitive Mark</title>
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap');

        :root {
            --bg: #000000;
            --text-main: #FFFFFF;
            --text-subtle: #A1A1A1;
            --border: #272727;
            --brand-primary: #FFFFFF;
            --brand-accent: #007AFF;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--bg);
            color: var(--text-main);
            margin: 0;
            padding: 4rem 2rem;
            line-height: 1.7;
            -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
            -moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 6rem;
        }

        .header h1 {
            font-size: 4rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            letter-spacing: -0.05em;
            margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
        }

        .header p {
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            color: var(--text-subtle);
            max-width: 650px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .concept-presentation {
            background: #0A0A0A;
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 1.5rem;
            padding: 5rem 4rem;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .logo-display {
            width: 250px;
            height: 250px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-bottom: 4rem;
            position: relative;
        }

        .logo-svg {
            width: 180px;
            height: 180px;
            overflow: visible;
        }
        
        .logo-svg .shape {
            transition: transform 0.5s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
            transform-origin: center;
        }

        .logo-display:hover .c-shape {
            transform: rotate(-10deg);
        }
        .logo-display:hover .dot-shape {
            transform: scale(1.2) rotate(10deg);
        }
        
        .logo-info {
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 600px;
        }

        .logo-info h2 {
            font-size: 2.75rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: -0.04em;
            margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
        }

        .logo-info p {
            font-size: 1.15rem;
            color: var(--text-subtle);
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }
        
        .logo-info .highlight {
            color: var(--brand-accent);
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .divider {
            width: 100px;
            height: 1px;
            background-color: var(--border);
            margin: 3rem auto;
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            body { padding: 2rem 1rem; }
            .concept-presentation { padding: 3rem 2rem; }
            .header h1 { font-size: 3rem; }
            .logo-info h2 { font-size: 2rem; }
        }

    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <header class="header">
            <h1>The Codeunia Mark</h1>
            <p>A definitive concept built on a powerful metaphor. This logo is designed to be intelligent, unique, and to establish a timeless, story-driven brand identity.</p>
        </header>

        <div class="concept-presentation">
            <div class="logo-display">
                <svg class="logo-svg" viewBox="0 0 200 200" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                    <!-- The 'C' for Code -->
                    <path class="shape c-shape" 
                        d="M165,100 A65,65 0 1 1 100,35"
                        fill="none" 
                        stroke="var(--brand-primary)" 
                        stroke-width="30" 
                        stroke-linecap="round"
                    />
                    
                    <!-- The Dot for Unia/Community -->
                    <circle class="shape dot-shape" cx="100" cy="165" r="15" fill="var(--brand-accent)"/>
                </svg>
            </div>
            
            <div class="logo-info">
                <h2>The Unia Point</h2>
                <p>
                    This logo is a symbol of <span class="highlight">Focus</span>, <span class="highlight">Completion</span>, and <span class="highlight">Community</span>. It is a modern, minimalist mark that is confident, clean, and conceptually strong.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="divider"></div>

            <div class="logo-info">
                <h2>The Logic</h2>
                <p>
                    The primary shape is a strong, unmistakable **'C' for Code**. It represents the world of programmingâ€”the structure, the language, the environment.
                </p>
                <p>
                    The dot is the **Unia**: the community, the individual developer, the focal point. It is the spark of life that completes the code and gives it purpose. The story is clear and powerful: **The community is the essential point that completes the world of code.**
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
